column5: I finally had an opportunity and the time to get up to see some great friends.  Arriving on Wednesday and only staying till Friday didn't give us a lot of time to catch up, however it did give me a few moments to cast a line off the dock. My gawd am I jealous of their beautiful piece of paradice.  Thanks for the invite...Can't wait to get out Muskie fishing next time.
Good stuff Bernadette. Glad you had a good time.
that first bass is a bruiser - looks like a great place to kick back and relax

Hey Jen, I'm Jay. Saw these pictures on a co-workers phone and was immediately jealous. That is a nice bass! (The Long Islands look pretty good too!) I'm always told I have to go up and do some fishing, maybe it's time to find some time! Nice results!
Thanks guys, it was good to finally get out and do some fishing.  The relaxing was truly welcomed as well.  Jay, no need to be jealous, I think you have a great co worker!
